# ── WHAT THIS FILE DOES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This CITATION.cff covers two citable objects housed in this repository:
#
#   1. The companion paper (primary citation — use this by default)
#   2. The AGI Evidence Vocabulary (agiev) and LegalRuleML encoding
#      (cite separately when reusing only the vocabulary/supplementary file)
#
# The "preferred-citation" block below points to the paper.
# The top-level fields describe the software/vocabulary artifact itself.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── TOP-LEVEL: vocabulary / software artifact ─────────────────────────────
message: >-
  If you use the AGI Evidence Vocabulary (agiev), the LegalRuleML
  encoding, or the compliance engine from this repository, please cite
  the companion paper using the preferred-citation block below.

